text: Maximus Inc., trademarked as MAXIMUS, is an American outsourcing company. It gives services about processing business. These services are for government health and human services agencies in the United States, Australia, Canada, Saudi Arabia, and the United Kingdom. Maximus focuses on government programs, such as Medicaid, the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP), health care reform, welfare-to-work, Medicare, child support, and other government programs. The company is in Reston, Virginia. It has more than 34,000 employees.
